Where was his son when they did take his eyes?
Come with my lady hither.
He is not here.
No, my good lord.
I met him back again.
Knows he the wickedness?
Ay, my good lord.
Twas he informed against him, And quit the house on purpose that their punishment Might have the freer course.
Gloucester, I live To thank thee for the love thou showed’st the king, And to revenge thine eyes.—Come hither, friend.
Tell me what more thou know’st.
